you need me *

18:34.214 --> 18:39.219
* You don't sing me
love songs *

18:39.286 --> 18:44.557
* Anymore

18:44.624 --> 18:47.860
( Applause )

18:50.597 --> 18:52.332
That was amazing!

18:52.399 --> 18:53.966
When you went low,
I took it up high.

18:54.033 --> 18:55.368
I can't believe it.

18:55.435 --> 18:57.170
We have to record
the next time we do this.
Yes.

18:57.237 --> 18:58.638
Without a doubt.
We should get clothes, though.

18:58.705 --> 18:59.706
We got to look
a little bit better.

18:59.772 --> 19:00.773
Yes, yes.
You know what I'm saying?

19:00.840 --> 19:01.974
Coordinating outfits.

19:02.041 --> 19:03.576
I'm telling you,
we're onto something here.

19:03.643 --> 19:05.612
Do you understand
the happiness we just
brought to these people?

19:05.678 --> 19:10.350
I think we should do this.
* Nessun dorma *

