( Applause )

20:03.470 --> 20:05.938
( Epic music plays
on television )

20:06.005 --> 20:07.874
Oh, man, he is good.

20:07.940 --> 20:09.942
His performance --
you just buy into it.

20:10.009 --> 20:11.110
Yep.

20:11.177 --> 20:12.545
It's like
he's not even acting.

20:12.612 --> 20:14.080
Yep.

20:14.146 --> 20:15.815
I mean, the fact that
he's working with Judi Dench

20:15.882 --> 20:18.585
doesn't hurt, either.

20:18.651 --> 20:19.919
( Dog barking )

20:19.986 --> 20:21.488
You hear that?
Right on cue.

20:21.554 --> 20:23.423
Yeah.

20:23.490 --> 20:25.325
By the way,
how sick are these?

20:25.392 --> 20:26.993
Incredible. You don't even
have to chew them.

20:27.059 --> 20:28.261
They just, like,
melt in your mouth.

20:28.328 --> 20:29.696
Right.
Like, in each bite,

20:29.762 --> 20:31.831
you get a little bit of sweet,
you get a little bit of hot.

20:31.898 --> 20:33.766
Mm-hmm.
These things are amazing.

20:33.833 --> 20:35.001
The best.

20:35.067 --> 20:37.136
How are the wings, boys?

20:42.842 --> 20:43.876
Eh, they're all right.

20:43.943 --> 20:46.045
I've had better.

20:46.112 --> 20:48.147
Yeah.
Thank you.

